OL,3,CFraud victim's daughter calls for
OL,4,Cgreater protections against scams
OL,6,FThe family has managed to recover most
OL,7,Fof the money but Valerie died last
OL,8,Fyear and did not know she could get
OL,9,Fthe money back.
OL,11,FScams targetting the elderly are on
OL,12,Fthe rise, partly due to the increasing
OL,13,Fuse of technology.
OL,15,FAccording to research by
OL,16,FMoneySuperMarket, someone aged 65 or
OL,17,Fover becomes a victim of fraud nearly
OL,18,Fevery minute in England and Wales.
