OL,3,CFraud victim's daughter calls for
OL,4,Cgreater protections against scams
OL,6,FAs well as postal and doorstep scams,
OL,7,Ffraudsters are exploiting digital
OL,8,Fplatforms such as email, text, and
OL,9,Fsocial media and now they're even
OL,10,Fusing AI-powered voice cloning.
OL,12,FDebbie is calling for supermarkets to
OL,13,Ftrain staff about gift card fraud and
OL,14,Fdisplay signs in their shops.
