OL,3,CFraud victim's daughter calls for
OL,4,Cgreater protections against scams
OL,6,FAlex Brewer, the MP for North East
OL,7,FHampshire, has raised the issue in
OL,8,FParliament. She is calling for
OL,9,Fincreased safeguarding processes in
OL,10,Fretail spaces to ensure that staff
OL,11,Fhave the necessary information and
OL,12,Fadvice to help them spot and avoid
OL,13,Fscams targeting the money of older or
OL,14,Fvulnerable individuals.
OL,16,FShe said: "In the UK, #1.2 billion was
OL,17,Flost to fraud and scams in 2024 and it
OL,18,Fwas similar the previous year, so we
OL,19,Fknow that this is a very, very
OL,20,Fexpensive problem."
