OL,6,FDebbie said: "I'm working with Alex
OL,7,Fand her team because it's very
OL,8,Fimportant for me to raise awareness to
OL,9,Fhelp stop them going through what my
OL,10,Ffamily have gone through."
OL,12,FHere are some ways to protect yourself
OL,13,Ffrom gift card fraud:
OL,15,F When speaking to someone online, be
OL,16,Faware that they may not be who they
OL,17,Fsay they are
OL,19,F Slow down. Before you send money,
OL,20,Ftalk with someone you trust
