OL,3,CFraud victim's daughter calls for
OL,4,Cgreater protections against scams
OL,6,F If you sent money to a scammer,
OL,7,Fcontact the company you used to send
OL,8,Fthe money (your bank, wire transfer
OL,9,Fservice, gift card company, or prepaid
OL,10,Fdebit card company). Tell them the
OL,11,Ftransaction was a fraud. Ask the
OL,12,Fcompany to reverse the transaction, if
OL,13,Fit's possible
OL,15,F Report your experience to the social
OL,16,Fmedia site in question. If a fraud has
OL,17,Falready taken place, report it to
OL,18,FAction Fraud and Police
OL,26,@nD@AbfwD@Abf
